  "description": "云枢资源生命周期监控看板：内存/线程/文件句柄/数据库连接的实时曲线与释放速率分析。指标来源 agent/monitoring/resource_monitor.py 上报的 yunshu_resource_usage gauge。",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "liveNow": false,
  "panels": [
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "Prometheus"
      },
      "description": "当前资源概览：内存峰值/活动线程/文件句柄/数据库连接。基于 yunshu_resource_usage gauge 最新值。",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 70
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 90
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "内存(MB)"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "unit",
                "value": "decmbytes"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "showPercentChange": false,
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "Prometheus"
          },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "max(yunshu_resource_usage{resource_type=\"memory\"}) / 1024 / 1024",
          "legendFormat": "内存(MB)",
          "range": false,
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "Prometheus"
          },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "max(yunshu_resource_usage{resource_type=\"thread\"})",
          "legendFormat": "活动线程",
          "range": false,
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "Prometheus"
          },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "max(yunshu_resource_usage{resource_type=\"file_handle\"})",
          "legendFormat": "文件句柄",
          "range": false,
          "refId": "C"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "Prometheus"
          },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum(yunshu_resource_usage{resource_type=\"db_connection\"})",
          "legendFormat": "数据库连接",
          "range": false,
          "refId": "D"
        }
      ],
      "title": "资源概览（当前值）",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "Prometheus"
      },
      "description": "内存使用趋势曲线：当前分配量与峰值对比。持续上升且无回落表明潜在泄漏。指标 yunshu_resource_usage{resource_type=memory}。",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 15,
            "gradientMode": "opacity",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "stacking": {
              "group": "A",
              "mode": "none"
            }
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 524288000
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 1073741824
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "bytes"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 6
      },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull", "max"],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "Prometheus"
          },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "max(yunshu_resource_usage{resource_type=\"memory\"})",
          "legendFormat": "当前内存",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "Prometheus"
          },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "max_over_time(yunshu_resource_usage{resource_type=\"memory\"}[1h])",
          "legendFormat": "1h 峰值",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "title": "内存使用趋势（含峰值回溯）",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "Prometheus"
      },
      "description": "内存释放速率曲线：正值表示增长（分配），负值表示释放。持续正值预示泄漏。基于 deriv() 计算变化率。",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 20,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 50000000
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "Bps"
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byRegexp",
              "options": "/释放/"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "custom.fillOpacity",
                "value": 30
              },
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "green"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 6
      },
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull", "max", "min"],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "Prometheus"
          },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "deriv(yunshu_resource_usage{resource_type=\"memory\"}[5m])",
          "legendFormat": "内存变化率(5m)",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "Prometheus"
          },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "rate(yunshu_resource_usage{resource_type=\"memory\"}[1m])",
          "legendFormat": "内存瞬时变化(1m)",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "title": "内存释放速率（增长/释放曲线）",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
